Blackheart bows. "Please sit down." A black circular table was loacated in 
the middle of the bridge. Each member of his crew had a seat with his name on 
it, and extra seats were placed for Tyrael and his second in command. 
Tyrael's name was on one of the seats. The  world map came up over the table. 
"All crew members please take your positions around the table."

--part1_149.3985f61.2b17ae1f_boundary
